1
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,039
Clan Elder.

2
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:33,200
Linglong,

3
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,090
sit down.

4
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:38,280
Linglong.

5
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:42,080
You are now

6
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,440
the new head of the Hu family.

7
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:47,080
I purposely asked you to stay

8
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,600
behind today

9
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:52,000
to give you some advice.

10
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,920
Don't ever forget

11
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:57,240
the vows you made

12
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:59,280
before the ancestors

13
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:01,440
of the Hu family,

14
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:03,100
to manage the family business

15
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,840
and never marry.

16
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:09,240
If you violate them,

17
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,440
then

18
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:14,440
I will punish you according to clan rules.

19
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,420
Do you understand?

20
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,640
Men!

21
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,920
Kick her out of the Hu family

22
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:21,920
and throw her into the mountains!

23
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:22,360
Stop!

24
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:23,720
As long as I'm here today,

25
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:25,160
don't even think about messing around.

26
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:26,520
Today, I, Hu Linglong,

27
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,320
if I can inherit the position of family head,

28
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:31,400
am willing to wholeheartedly manage the family business

29
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,360
and never marry.

30
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,400
This is my vow.

31
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,120
Linglong,

32
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,320
what do you mean by this?

33
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:37,320
Shut up. What are you talking about?

34
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,280
Xu Zhinian.

35
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,400
This doll

36
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,600
I secretly sewed behind my father's back.

37
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,480
My mother said

38
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:48,079
giving this doll stuffed with black tea

39
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:49,400
to the one you love

40
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,200
can ward off evil

41
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,660
and pray for his blessing.

42
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:58,640
Linglong.

43
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:02,440
Now the Hu family is beset with difficulties,

44
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,800
and foreign merchants are pressing us.

45
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:07,480
From now on, every step you take

46
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:10,960
must be careful.

47
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,380
Clan Elder,

48
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,400
I understand.

49
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,640
Sit down.

50
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,200
Why am I back here again?

51
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:44,160
Elder Sanshan.

52
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,400
Mr. Yamamoto,

53
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,160
what are you doing here?

54
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:49,640
We

55
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,600
have no cooperation with you,

56
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,770
and we don't welcome the Japanese.

57
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:54,800
Elder Sanshan,

58
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:56,880
I apologize for the abrupt intrusion

59
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:57,880
today.

60
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,720
I only heard

61
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:05,600
that the Hu family was having trouble deciding

62
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,930
on the next family head,

63
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,320
so I came

64
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:10,240
to put in a good word for Mr. Hu Wenyi.

65
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:10,880
Oh,

66
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,080
Mr. Yamamoto.

67
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,399
Unfortunately, you are a step too late.

68
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:19,200
Our new family head

69
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,360
has already been chosen.

70
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,520
Besides,

71
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:26,400
our Hu family's affairs

72
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:28,720
do not need

73
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,120
outsiders

74
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,760
to interfere.

75
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,440
Elder Sanshan,

76
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:39,600
please don't be so hostile towards me.

77
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,600
I came here this time

78
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,680
mainly to talk with the Hu family

79
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,640
about cooperation

80
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:45,640
and business.

81
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,400
Haha.

82
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,880
Doing business with the Japanese

83
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,320
is like inviting a wolf into the house.

84
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,480
For hundreds of years,

85
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,880
the Japanese have never given up their ambition to subjugate China.

86
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:59,880
They massacred our compatriots and trampled our homeland.

87
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:00,720
Their crimes are too numerous

88
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,520
to record.

89
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:03,050
You must not agree with him.

90
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,000
What...

91
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,840
what's wrong?

92
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:06,880
Why can't I see anything?

93
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:07,440
Hey,

94
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,920
did you hear what I said?

95
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,640
I...

96
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,560
why do I suddenly feel

97
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,240
so sleepy?

98
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:27,880
Since our Hu family has a new head,

99
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:29,840
then

100
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:32,240
all business dealings

101
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,520
will still

102
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,200
depend on

103
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,800
the new head's wishes.

104
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,960
This...

105
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:46,920
Miss Hu.

106
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,920
You Japanese do evil things on Chinese soil.

107
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,920
We will

108
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,380
never cooperate with you.

109
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,640
Please leave.

110
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,520
You don't know what's good for you.

111
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:09,880
There will be plenty of time

112
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,740
for you to slowly regret it later.

113
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,320
Hmph.

114
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:25,400
The voice I heard today

115
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,730
seems to have come from this jade pendant.

116
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:29,040
Was it you speaking?

117
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,840
Say something!

118
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:37,000
Strange.

119
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:40,760
Hey,

120
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,920
can you hear me?

121
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,480
Words appeared.

122
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,520
Fulfill the unfulfilled wish

123
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,880
to open this door.

124
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,960
This means

125
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:58,360
I have to help Hu Linglong fulfill her wish.

126
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,000
Hey.

127
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,640
Ah! A monster!

128
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,920
A monster?

129
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:14,380
Have you ever seen such a beautiful monster?

130
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,320
You don't really look like a monster,

131
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:22,720
but I clearly saw you appear out of thin air.

132
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,720
Are you the one

133
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,250
who took over my body today?

134
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,160
Yes,

135
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,040
it's me.

136
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,720
I don't know what happened either.

137
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,380
I clearly came from the mod...

138
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:36,920
Could it be that I can't

139
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,760
talk about modern times?

140
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:41,120
No wonder the illusion disappeared

141
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,380
and I fainted earlier.

142
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,840
I am

143
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:47,360
a fairy sent down from heaven.

144
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,800
I descended to the mortal world to lend you a hand,

145
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:52,400
so you can securely sit as the head of the Hu family.

146
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:54,080
If it weren't for my help today,

147
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:57,010
I'm afraid you would be wandering the streets by now.

148
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,480
Help me?

149
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,160
You took over my body!

150
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:00,920
The things you said

151
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:01,720
and did

152
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,050
have made me miserable.

153
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:04,960
Sigh,

154
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:05,960
let's not talk about this anymore.

155
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:06,920
Oh, right.

156
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:09,280
Do you have any wishes you want to fulfill?

157
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:11,560
I wouldn't tell you even if I did.

158
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,520
Hurry up.

159
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,560
Tell me.

160
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,360
Answer me.

161
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,220
Say something!

162
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:22,120
Hey!

163
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,160
Hey!

164
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:24,960
Hey!

165
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,080
Hey!

166
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:30,560
Hey, hey!

167
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:49,680
Brother was pushed into the water!

168
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:50,600
Dr. Xue,

169
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,920
regarding my son drowning today,

170
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,760
you must not reveal a word to anyone.

171
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:55,800
Why are you wearing boys' clothes?

172
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:57,280
You are obviously a girl.

173
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:58,840
From now on, these dresses,

174
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,080
you must not wear them anymore.

175
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,480
Not a single piece can be kept.

176
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,560
Father.

177
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,480
Long'er.

178
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:22,920
Long'er.

179
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,080
Mother.

180
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:34,480
Long'er.

181
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,320
Why are you crying?

182
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,000
Mother,

183
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,120
I'm fine.

184
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,200
I just woke up.

185
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,120
These jewelry

186
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,680
and cosmetics,

187
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:52,200
I picked them out for you myself.

188
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,680
This dress,

189
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:08,320
it was your favorite

190
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,440
when you were little.

191
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,680
Didn't my father

192
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,360
throw them all away back then?

193
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:17,720
He did throw them away.

194
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:18,960
But,

195
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:21,200
I picked this one back up.

196
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:26,480
This was the first dress I ever bought for you.

197
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,970
I couldn't bear to part with it.

198
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:43,680
Long'er,

199
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:46,320
in this life,

200
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:49,130
there are many things beyond our control.

201
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:51,000
It's true for you,

202
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,680
for me,

203
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:54,240
and for your father.

204
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:57,720
But no matter what you become,

205
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,480
you will always be my daughter.

206
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,880
Now,

207
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:05,560
you can finally show yourself as a woman.

208
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:07,960
I'm happy for you.

209
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,000
And even more,

210
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:12,600
I worry for you.

211
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:13,720
Mother,

212
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,280
why do you say that?

213
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:17,400
If one day you find

214
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:19,720
that returning to being a woman

215
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,440
isn't necessarily happier

216
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,280
or freer than before,

217
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,480
when that time comes,

218
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:26,600
what will you do?

219
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:30,840
Never mind,

220
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:32,740
let's not talk about this.

221
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,200
Come,

222
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:33,880
Long'er,

223
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,200
come and sit.

224
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:38,380
Let me help you with your makeup and hair.

225
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:46,960
Father,

226
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,160
how are you still in the mood

227
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:49,520
to drink tea and read here?

228
00:11:49,520 --> 00:11:51,180
What are you panicking about?

229
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:55,120
Hu Linglong has already taken

230
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,320
the position of the head of the family.

231
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,040
We need to find a way to deal with her.

232
00:11:58,040 --> 00:11:58,570
Alright.

233
00:11:59,200 --> 00:11:59,840
You may go.

234
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:00,400
Yes.

235
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,520
It's only been one night.

236
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,560
She can't make much trouble.

237
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:08,160
Don't act rashly.

238
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,900
Once we make a move,

239
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:11,440
we will take her life.
